                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330214-222-off1246 t18330214-222-crimeloc1249"></join>. On the 29th of January, about four o'clock in the afternoon, I hung these boots on the door-post, and in about five minutes I saw the prisoner take them off the book - I ran and overtook him, and saw him throw them down; I am certain they were my father's - he went about five yards before he threw them down, on seeing me.</p>
               <p>JOHN YATES. I am an officer. I received him in charge.(Property produced and sworn to.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. 
               <persName id="t18330214-222-person1965">
